NOTE ON THIRD-PARTY MODELS
--------------------------
Fuser does not ship model weights. The ONNX models it downloads at runtime
(InsightFace inswapper_128, buffalo_l, GFPGAN, CodeFormer, GPEN,
RestoreFormer++, etc.) are distributed by their respective authors under their
own licenses, several of which are restricted to non-commercial / research use.
You are responsible for reviewing and complying with each model's license and
for using face-swapping technology ethically and lawfully (with consent).
